# Surge 5 RULE-SET (DOMAIN-SUFFIX rules)
# Target Policy: Proxy
# Purpose: Force proxy for specific education domains requested.
#
# Usage (Surge):
#   [Rule]
#   RULE-SET,https://your-domain-or-raw-link/edu.list,Proxy
#
# Notes:
# - Uses DOMAIN-SUFFIX to cover all subdomains (e.g., www, mail, canvas, etc.).
# - If any school uses a different primary domain, tell me and I’ll add it.

# Joliet Junior College
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,jjc.edu

# Campus
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,canvaslms.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,icampus.instructure.com

# California State University, Northridge
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,csun.edu

# Spokane Community College (district domain commonly used)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,scc.spokane.edu
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,spokane.edu

# Santa Fe College
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,sfcollege.edu
